  "text": "for any \u03bb \u2208 R p + and any x \u2208 X. Denote by X \u00d7 \u039b = X 1 \u00d7 \u00b7 \u00b7 \u00b7 \u00d7 X m \u00d7 \u039b the set of all optimal primal-dual pairs. Under Assumptions 1-3, it was shown in [CITATION_1] that the set of optimal dual solutions \u039b is bounded, and hence sup \u03bb\u2208\u039b \u03bb is finite.",
